description: Igor and Michaela ventured all the way from Slovakia to LA to introduce the West Coast to true traditional Slovak cuisine. These two took age-old family recipes, gave them a modern gastronomical twist, and now Duck in the Truck is serving up the best Gourmet Eastern European fare you can find in the whole city, let alone the streets. After trying this truck’s homemade specialties, like their Potato Wraps, Dumplings, and of course their delicious duck...you’ll be sure to waddle away happy.
name: Duck in the Truck
